Add register method for JSON-Home data- index/create

This patch adds register methods for registering json-home
data for resources and make that available to register json-home data.

This patch adds support for index/create only and follow up patches
will add support for show/delete/updates where resource id also will be
added in json-home data.

json-home data for index/create will looks like-

{
    "http://docs.openstack.org/api/openstack-compute/2.1/rel/servers": {
      "href-template": "/v2.1/{project_id}/servers",
      "href-vars": {
        "project_id": "http://docs.openstack.org/api/openstack-compute/2.1/param/project_id"
      }
    },
    "http://docs.openstack.org/api/openstack-compute/2.1/rel/flavors": {
      "href-template": "/v2.1/{project_id}/flavors",
      "href-vars": {
        "project_id": "http://docs.openstack.org/api/openstack-compute/2.1/param/project_id"
      }
    },
    [..]
}

